<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Dear EchoMarket <%= @userType %>,  <%= @userAlias %></h1>
    <p>The EchoMarket Lender, <%= @lenderAlias %>,  has offered the following item, which may be of interest to you: </p>
      <br/> 
    
      <p>Item Category: <% @itemCategory %></p>
      <br/> 
      
      <p>Item Description: <% @itemDescription %></p>
      <br/> 
      
      <p>Item Condition: <% @itemCondition %></p>
      <br/> 
      
      <p>Item Image: <img src=<% @itemImage %> /></p>
      <br/> 
      
      <p>If you would like more information, please follow this link, or copy/paste it to your browser address bar: <% @contact %></p>
      <br/> 
    
      <p>If you wish to no longer receive notifications of offered Lender items, please follow this link, or copy/paste it to your browser address bar: <% @noNotification %></p>
      <br/> 
	
      <p>Otherwise, EchoMarket thanks for your participation.  Your service for borrowing, lending, donating and trading goods!</p>

  </body>

</html>